"{\"uid\": \"sputnikglobe.com-20240728-major-us-tech-company-to-pull-advertising-from-paris-olympics-after-last-supper-mockery-1119539511.html\", \"text\": \"European observer 'would love to work for Sputnik', move to Russia after freak show Olympics opening ceremony in France\\\"I would love to work for Sputnik in Russia and would not hesitate a second to swap my Italian passport [for] a Russian passport,\\\" Angelo Giuliano\\u2026https://t.co/LK6ZZ2lVRPpic.twitter.com/9g9SPGiFbi  France is hosting the 2024 Summer Olympics from July 26 to August 11, with most of the events taking place in Paris and its suburbs.\"}"